Generate a single markdown file for GitHub with ```markdown refix: For the typescript library material-ui in version v5.14.17 with a problem in datepicker. I  created the repository https://github.com/joel/repocenas.git to have an example of the problem so everyone can test it. Topics to have: Issue Description: Problem: Repository Example: Reproduction Steps this typescript project

```markdown
# Issue Description
The datepicker in material-ui is not functioning as expected in the v5.14.17 version.

# Problem
The problem occurs when trying to use the datepicker component to select a date. It either does not open the date picker modal, or it does not allow selecting a date.

# Repository Example
I created a repository at https://github.com/joel/repocenas.git to serve as an example of the problem. This repository contains a minimal setup to reproduce the issue.

# Reproduction Steps
1. Clone the repository: https://github.com/joel/repocenas.git
2. Install dependencies and build the project.
3. Run the project and navigate to the component using the datepicker.
4. Try to open the datepicker and select a date to see the issue in action.
```
